projects.name: Driver Drowsiness Detection And Accident Alert System
projects.description: A Level 4 Project is a scalable project deployed in a production setting on a Latest Tech Stack JAVA,XML,SQL Lite. It should be capable of handling a load of up to X+ simultaneous users using Horizontal scaling. One should have a deep understanding of System Design Principles to build a Backend of the Project. Building a Level-4 Project helps you to land directly in top 0.2 percent of India.
